Package gw.plugin.preupdate.prioritized

Class PrioritizedPreUpdateContext<T extends KeyableBean>

java.lang.Object
gw.plugin.preupdate.prioritized.PrioritizedPreUpdateContext<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The bean type that will be processed.
public final class PrioritizedPreUpdateContext<T extends KeyableBean> extends Object
Represents the pre-update context for a specific bean type in the current bundle.

This context holds the lists of inserted, updated, and removed beans that are part of the current bundle.

The context encapsulates the necessary data for performing pre-update operations in PrioritizedPreUpdateExecutor objects, including:

  • Inserted beans, newly created in the current bundle.
  • Updated beans, modified objects in the current bundle.
  • Removed beans, deleted objects in the current bundle.
